         <abstract id="aspace_3d4e7f534f7e7fa5e5e96d94897fd69e">The materials consist of memorabilia, photographs, artifacts, and an engraving documenting Franklin Lindley Couch's (Yale 1917) extracurricular activities while a student at Yale. Included are materials documenting the Yale Courant staff, Beta Theta Pi fraternity, Calcium Light Night, and the Yale Field Artillery in World War I.</abstract>
    
      </did>
      <odd id="aspace_2e9366cb193dc731a794912086ebccd2">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 45 (YRG 45), Yale objects and memorabilia.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_f09170095c4ab225412b00bebb495286">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The materials were a gift of Mr. and Mrs. Robert B. Couch, 2001.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_058a66091b99db5e03e410bc55faaf72">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_974b6279a2faf614cec1894a08d004b3">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Franklin Lindley Couch, Class of 1917, Yale College, Memorabilia (RU 864). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_a3f3c14ab8309c26a2f0bb1f77f04b37">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Arrange by topic.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_89c95925ebab74c39b1bce5c5b457eae">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of memorabilia, photographs, artifacts, and an engraving documenting Franklin Lindley Couch's (Yale 1917) extracurricular activities while a student at Yale. Included are materials documenting the Yale Courant staff, Beta Theta Pi fraternity, Calcium Light Night, and the Yale Field Artillery in World War I.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
